1
00:00:40,000 --> 00:00:42,440
Ji.

2
00:01:02,240 --> 00:01:03,800
The Medicine God Society's debt to my family

3
00:01:03,800 --> 00:01:05,200
should be paid.

4
00:01:05,920 --> 00:01:06,720
Be careful.

5
00:01:09,200 --> 00:01:10,000
I'm fine.

6
00:01:11,560 --> 00:01:14,200
I just want to stop the Medicine God.

7
00:01:15,360 --> 00:01:16,600
Ten years ago,

8
00:01:16,720 --> 00:01:19,000
when Yingtian Prefecture held the Medicine God temple fair,

9
00:01:19,000 --> 00:01:20,920
I was afraid Dayou would be chosen by the Medicine God,

10
00:01:20,920 --> 00:01:22,120
so I didn't let him go.

11
00:01:22,120 --> 00:01:23,960
But that night, someone came.

12
00:01:24,160 --> 00:01:26,280
I want your son to join the Medicine God Society

13
00:01:26,280 --> 00:01:28,000
to become a medicine boy,

14
00:01:28,080 --> 00:01:29,600
bring honor to your ancestors,

15
00:01:29,600 --> 00:01:31,400
and benefit the world.

16
00:01:32,280 --> 00:01:33,920
Dayou won't go.

17
00:01:33,920 --> 00:01:35,050
You'd better leave.

18
00:01:48,880 --> 00:01:49,680
My wife.

19
00:01:50,160 --> 00:01:51,240
Since then,

20
00:01:51,680 --> 00:01:52,960
Dayou went missing.

21
00:01:53,240 --> 00:01:54,640
It wasn't until two years ago

22
00:01:54,640 --> 00:01:55,880
that I found him.

23
00:01:56,520 --> 00:01:57,840
So I locked him up.

24
00:01:57,880 --> 00:01:58,680
Dayou.

25
00:01:59,080 --> 00:02:01,200
What's with the portrait in the secret room?

26
00:02:01,200 --> 00:02:02,480
I always felt

27
00:02:03,120 --> 00:02:05,880
someone was using the rumors of the Plague Boy to harm people.

28
00:02:05,880 --> 00:02:06,760
So,

29
00:02:07,080 --> 00:02:08,800
I followed the clues from the victims

30
00:02:08,800 --> 00:02:09,960
to track down the culprit,

31
00:02:09,960 --> 00:02:11,680
but couldn't find any leads.

32
00:02:12,000 --> 00:02:13,400
When I learned that the Duchess

33
00:02:13,400 --> 00:02:14,480
was also poisoned,

34
00:02:15,880 --> 00:02:17,480
I wanted to come and help.

35
00:02:21,400 --> 00:02:22,880
So you've been researching an antidote

36
00:02:22,880 --> 00:02:23,880
to save Qu Dayou.

37
00:02:24,880 --> 00:02:26,440
No wonder there are traces of alchemy

38
00:02:26,440 --> 00:02:27,500
in the secret room.

39
00:02:27,880 --> 00:02:29,120
This child Dayou,

40
00:02:29,400 --> 00:02:31,280
although born with a medicinal constitution,

41
00:02:31,280 --> 00:02:32,600
the plague won't take his life.

42
00:02:32,600 --> 00:02:34,800
But what I fear most is someone using him

43
00:02:34,880 --> 00:02:36,560
to bring the plague back,

44
00:02:36,920 --> 00:02:38,850
causing widespread devastation.

45
00:02:46,360 --> 00:02:46,880
Oh no.

46
00:02:47,320 --> 00:02:48,980
Qu Dayou has already escaped.

47
00:02:49,079 --> 00:02:50,610
We need to find him quickly.

48
00:02:51,120 --> 00:02:51,880
I suspect

49
00:02:52,200 --> 00:02:54,600
Qu Dayou is already in that person's hands.

50
00:02:54,600 --> 00:02:55,800
It was also that person

51
00:02:55,800 --> 00:02:57,200
who led us to scare Qu Dayou away.

52
00:02:57,200 --> 00:02:58,060
Without delay,

53
00:02:58,280 --> 00:02:59,360
let's split up.

54
00:02:59,560 --> 00:03:01,120
I'll research the antidote just in case,

55
00:03:01,120 --> 00:03:01,960
and you gather clues

56
00:03:01,960 --> 00:03:02,960
to find the truth.

57
00:03:24,680 --> 00:03:25,400
Uncle.

58
00:03:25,800 --> 00:03:28,320
These reagents were left by Prince Zhuoran.

59
00:03:28,560 --> 00:03:29,680
I am inexperienced,

60
00:03:29,680 --> 00:03:30,680
and do not know their uses.

61
00:03:30,680 --> 00:03:32,480
Perhaps you can use them, Uncle.

62
00:03:34,120 --> 00:03:35,200
Ptaquiloside,

63
00:03:36,040 --> 00:03:37,240
thiaminase,

64
00:03:37,600 --> 00:03:38,760
and lead compounds.

65
00:03:40,360 --> 00:03:42,690
No wonder it worsens mental instability.

66
00:03:44,560 --> 00:03:45,880
The evolution of this virus

67
00:03:45,880 --> 00:03:47,280
is clearly man-made too.

68
00:03:54,680 --> 00:03:56,079
The test results are out.

69
00:03:57,240 --> 00:03:58,520
Boiled mugwort ash

70
00:03:58,680 --> 00:03:59,880
can absorb toxins.

71
00:04:00,160 --> 00:04:00,960
Plus,

72
00:04:01,320 --> 00:04:01,840
Qu San used

73
00:04:01,840 --> 00:04:02,600
Shanghan Lun

74
00:04:03,000 --> 00:04:04,600
to develop an emetic method.

75
00:04:04,840 --> 00:04:07,760
Combined with Prince Zhuoran's antibacterial medicine,

76
00:04:07,760 --> 00:04:10,480
it should achieve a targeted detoxifying effect.

77
00:04:10,480 --> 00:04:11,920
I'm glad I could help you, Uncle.

78
00:04:11,920 --> 00:04:13,520
Thanks to you too, Nephew.

79
00:04:15,240 --> 00:04:16,480
That's not right.

80
00:04:21,279 --> 00:04:22,079
Look.

81
00:04:22,680 --> 00:04:23,920
The time of the crimes

82
00:04:24,080 --> 00:04:25,840
and the locations don't match.

83
00:04:32,520 --> 00:04:33,580
At the first watch,

84
00:04:33,640 --> 00:04:34,840
it was Xunman Street.

85
00:04:35,960 --> 00:04:38,420
The second watch at the chamber of commerce.

86
00:04:38,680 --> 00:04:41,540
The third watch at the Temple of the God of Medicine.

87
00:04:55,680 --> 00:04:56,480
That's right.

88
00:04:56,680 --> 00:04:57,680
It should be him.

89
00:05:18,360 --> 00:05:19,200
Stop!

90
00:05:33,360 --> 00:05:34,320
How did you

91
00:05:34,480 --> 00:05:36,280
find me?

92
00:05:37,760 --> 00:05:39,120
Every time you committed a crime,

93
00:05:39,120 --> 00:05:40,880
you announced the time early

94
00:05:41,159 --> 00:05:42,840
to make it easier to poison them

95
00:05:42,840 --> 00:05:44,280
and create an alibi.

96
00:05:45,040 --> 00:05:47,280
The time and place of the crime

97
00:05:47,400 --> 00:05:48,240
don't match.

98
00:05:55,159 --> 00:05:57,280
Time passed so quickly.

99
00:05:59,960 --> 00:06:00,680
In addition,

100
00:06:00,680 --> 00:06:03,160
the identical shoe prints found at the crime scenes

101
00:06:03,160 --> 00:06:04,220
have been compared

102
00:06:04,480 --> 00:06:06,480
and proved to be from straw sandals.

103
00:06:07,440 --> 00:06:09,680
You also used your identity as a night watchman

104
00:06:09,680 --> 00:06:11,540
to report the scene immediately,

105
00:06:11,880 --> 00:06:14,040
deliberately framing Qu San

106
00:06:14,280 --> 00:06:15,680
to confuse us.

107
00:06:22,360 --> 00:06:25,090
The God of Medicine has done so much for the world,

108
00:06:26,880 --> 00:06:28,000
yet they

109
00:06:29,160 --> 00:06:31,760
have no gratitude.

110
00:06:34,840 --> 00:06:37,170
They even wanted to tear down this temple.

111
00:06:40,159 --> 00:06:42,200
I had to send them to their deaths.

112
00:07:01,880 --> 00:07:03,280
The God of Medicine will bless you

113
00:07:03,280 --> 00:07:04,480
and cure your plague.

114
00:07:09,240 --> 00:07:10,760
Thank you. Thank you.

115
00:07:10,760 --> 00:07:12,480
Thank you for saving my life.

116
00:07:13,760 --> 00:07:14,680
I will

117
00:07:15,400 --> 00:07:16,730
repay you in the future.

118
00:07:17,080 --> 00:07:18,880
Even if I die ten thousand times,

119
00:07:19,080 --> 00:07:20,880
I will go through fire and water.

120
00:07:21,360 --> 00:07:22,690
Remember what you said.

121
00:07:27,640 --> 00:07:30,440
Some children are incarnations of the Plague Boy.

122
00:07:30,480 --> 00:07:31,640
They are born

123
00:07:31,800 --> 00:07:33,120
filthy and evil.

124
00:07:33,480 --> 00:07:36,140
But the Medicine God Society tests drugs on them

125
00:07:36,320 --> 00:07:38,880
to save more people like you.

126
00:07:55,480 --> 00:07:57,810
I have been guarding here all these years,

127
00:07:57,880 --> 00:08:00,480
hoping to continue the Medicine God's legacy.

128
00:08:00,840 --> 00:08:02,240
But they

129
00:08:02,840 --> 00:08:05,080
are ungrateful.

130
00:08:08,480 --> 00:08:10,540
I punished them for the Medicine God.

131
00:08:11,480 --> 00:08:13,720
What's wrong with that?

132
00:08:18,720 --> 00:08:20,050
I have read the records.

133
00:08:20,680 --> 00:08:22,240
The plague ten years ago

134
00:08:22,520 --> 00:08:23,440
came suddenly

135
00:08:23,440 --> 00:08:24,520
and went suddenly.

136
00:08:25,280 --> 00:08:28,040
It was clearly orchestrated by the Medicine God Society.

137
00:08:28,040 --> 00:08:28,960
They harm people first,

138
00:08:28,960 --> 00:08:30,080
then save them.

139
00:08:30,320 --> 00:08:32,520
Just to make you blindly loyal,

140
00:08:32,559 --> 00:08:34,080
and turn you into an accomplice

141
00:08:34,080 --> 00:08:35,880
to experiment on living people.

142
00:08:37,720 --> 00:08:38,919
Impossible.

143
00:08:41,559 --> 00:08:42,760
Impossible.

144
00:08:44,960 --> 00:08:46,280
Nonsense.

145
00:08:48,480 --> 00:08:49,800
Qu Dayou

146
00:08:50,160 --> 00:08:52,240
is clearly a Plague Child.

147
00:08:52,920 --> 00:08:53,580
Otherwise,

148
00:08:54,560 --> 00:08:56,440
why didn't he die?

149
00:08:57,880 --> 00:09:00,140
I am following the Medicine God's orders

150
00:09:00,160 --> 00:09:01,920
to eliminate a menace.

151
00:09:02,080 --> 00:09:04,480
There are no Plague Children in this world,

152
00:09:04,520 --> 00:09:07,320
but true demons like the Medicine God Society do exist.

153
00:09:07,320 --> 00:09:08,800
Because Qu Dayou has

154
00:09:09,080 --> 00:09:10,120
antibodies to the plague in his body,

155
00:09:10,120 --> 00:09:11,780
which can help develop a cure.

156
00:09:11,920 --> 00:09:13,120
If you kill him,

157
00:09:13,480 --> 00:09:15,680
you will be the true sinner of all time.

158
00:09:16,720 --> 00:09:17,520
No.

159
00:09:21,720 --> 00:09:22,520
No.

160
00:09:27,040 --> 00:09:28,000
The Medicine God

161
00:09:28,280 --> 00:09:30,840
wouldn't lie to me.

162
00:09:39,160 --> 00:09:41,880
You are the one who is lying.

163
00:09:48,280 --> 00:09:49,400
Now.

164
00:09:50,080 --> 00:09:53,080
I will take the Plague Boy with me

165
00:09:53,880 --> 00:09:56,240
to see the God of Medicine.

166
00:10:11,280 --> 00:10:12,740
Let's go to Qu San's place.

167
00:10:19,280 --> 00:10:21,840
Disaster! Disaster!

168
00:10:22,360 --> 00:10:24,160
You burned the Temple of the God of Medicine

169
00:10:24,160 --> 00:10:26,080
and saved the Plague Boy.

170
00:10:26,240 --> 00:10:28,680
Now the people are worried that the plague will return.

171
00:10:28,680 --> 00:10:29,200
They are all

172
00:10:29,200 --> 00:10:32,360
blocking the outside, demanding an explanation!

173
00:10:32,560 --> 00:10:33,680
Who is so bold

174
00:10:33,680 --> 00:10:35,410
as to cause trouble at my manor?

175
00:10:36,000 --> 00:10:36,680
Wait.

176
00:10:36,960 --> 00:10:38,560
You took over the Temple of the God of Medicine earlier.

177
00:10:38,560 --> 00:10:39,880
They haven't swallowed their anger yet.

178
00:10:39,880 --> 00:10:41,880
Going out now will just add fuel to the fire.

179
00:10:41,880 --> 00:10:42,680
That's right.

180
00:10:42,800 --> 00:10:44,040
The commoners are mostly simple.

181
00:10:44,040 --> 00:10:46,080
They firmly believe in the God of Medicine and the Plague Boy.

182
00:10:46,080 --> 00:10:47,840
It's hard to explain it clearly in a short time.

183
00:10:47,840 --> 00:10:49,160
You must know that they believe in ghosts and gods

184
00:10:49,160 --> 00:10:51,220
more than they believe in you nobles.

185
00:10:51,240 --> 00:10:52,560
If they have to choose,

186
00:10:52,640 --> 00:10:54,680
they will definitely follow the former.

187
00:10:54,680 --> 00:10:55,880
The best way right now

188
00:10:56,000 --> 00:10:57,280
is to cure the Duchess.

189
00:10:57,280 --> 00:10:58,640
This will prove the plague is over

190
00:10:58,640 --> 00:10:59,700
and reassure them.

191
00:11:00,880 --> 00:11:01,610
Don't worry.

192
00:11:01,920 --> 00:11:03,920
I asked Jianqin to get the medicine.

193
00:11:09,920 --> 00:11:13,520
The young master is still waiting for me to go back and save lives.

194
00:11:26,040 --> 00:11:26,720
Come here.

195
00:11:27,000 --> 00:11:29,600
The people outside are getting more and more agitated.

196
00:11:29,600 --> 00:11:31,160
I think our only option now

197
00:11:31,480 --> 00:11:33,280
is to hand over Liu Chuan first.

198
00:11:33,480 --> 00:11:35,040
Treated as the culprit.

199
00:11:35,240 --> 00:11:36,900
How could you do this, Father?

200
00:11:37,320 --> 00:11:40,360
Although the princess caused this,

201
00:11:40,640 --> 00:11:42,560
she is of noble birth.

202
00:11:42,560 --> 00:11:43,480
As for you,

203
00:11:43,480 --> 00:11:44,600
you are my daughter.

204
00:11:44,600 --> 00:11:46,000
I just took office.

205
00:11:46,080 --> 00:11:47,880
I will abandon him.

206
00:11:49,960 --> 00:11:51,920
You are really a cunning old fox.

207
00:11:52,200 --> 00:11:54,440
You send me to die and take the blame.

208
00:11:57,200 --> 00:11:58,360
I can't care about that much now.

209
00:11:58,360 --> 00:12:00,040
Gather all the guards and servants

210
00:12:00,040 --> 00:12:01,080
to suppress the rioters.

211
00:12:01,080 --> 00:12:02,760
Your Highness, do not act rashly.

212
00:12:02,760 --> 00:12:03,960
Liuchuan is my man.

213
00:12:03,960 --> 00:12:06,760
You must look at the master before hitting his dog.

214
00:12:06,840 --> 00:12:07,640
Young Master.

215
00:12:08,640 --> 00:12:09,440
Young Master.

216
00:12:09,480 --> 00:12:10,560
Jianqin, you are finally here.

217
00:12:10,560 --> 00:12:12,620
If you came any later, I would be dead.

218
00:12:13,760 --> 00:12:15,400
Greetings, Your Highness Prince Jia.

219
00:12:15,400 --> 00:12:15,880
Rise.

220
00:12:15,880 --> 00:12:16,520
Brother.

221
00:12:16,640 --> 00:12:17,120
Yi'er.

222
00:12:17,480 --> 00:12:18,280
Brother.

223
00:12:18,760 --> 00:12:19,960
Don't panic, Yi'er.

224
00:12:20,640 --> 00:12:22,880
I have calmed the commoners outside.

225
00:12:23,160 --> 00:12:25,200
You are used to being willful and bossy.

226
00:12:25,200 --> 00:12:26,960
You almost caused a disaster today.

227
00:12:26,960 --> 00:12:28,400
Brother, Mother...

228
00:12:29,000 --> 00:12:30,040
Your Highness, please see clearly.

229
00:12:30,040 --> 00:12:30,880
Today's incident

230
00:12:30,880 --> 00:12:33,000
was all caused by that kid surnamed Liu.

231
00:12:33,000 --> 00:12:35,930
It has nothing to do with the Princess and the others.

232
00:12:36,000 --> 00:12:37,600
So he is Prince Jia.

233
00:12:37,760 --> 00:12:39,000
No wonder he looks extraordinary

234
00:12:39,000 --> 00:12:40,200
and elegant.

235
00:12:47,240 --> 00:12:49,500
The Duchess's condition is also stable.

236
00:12:49,600 --> 00:12:50,400
Mother.

237
00:12:52,080 --> 00:12:52,800
Insolent!

238
00:12:53,240 --> 00:12:54,370
Pay your respects to

239
00:12:54,560 --> 00:12:55,960
His Highness Prince Jia.

240
00:12:57,800 --> 00:12:59,560
You must be Liu Chuan.

241
00:12:59,600 --> 00:13:01,130
I have heard much about you.

242
00:13:01,280 --> 00:13:02,680
His Majesty bestowed upon you the Willow Leaf Golden Knife

243
00:13:02,680 --> 00:13:04,200
to dissect any corpse in the world.

244
00:13:04,200 --> 00:13:04,880
Seeing you today,

245
00:13:04,880 --> 00:13:06,940
you truly live up to your reputation.

246
00:13:07,000 --> 00:13:08,240
For saving my mother's life,

247
00:13:08,240 --> 00:13:10,170
I will never forget your kindness.

248
00:13:10,800 --> 00:13:12,000
Am I that famous?

249
00:13:12,600 --> 00:13:13,600
You flatter me.

250
00:13:13,880 --> 00:13:14,800
You certainly have my royal brother's

251
00:13:14,800 --> 00:13:16,130
outstanding demeanor.

252
00:13:16,200 --> 00:13:17,440
Meeting you today,

253
00:13:18,400 --> 00:13:20,400
why don't we become sworn brothers?

254
00:13:21,080 --> 00:13:22,200
Your Highness, please be perceptive.

255
00:13:22,200 --> 00:13:23,760
This Young Master Liu

256
00:13:23,760 --> 00:13:25,560
is indeed a rare talent.

257
00:13:25,560 --> 00:13:27,800
And he is my future son-in-law.

258
00:13:29,600 --> 00:13:30,400
I am hungry.

259
00:13:30,400 --> 00:13:31,280
Let's go.

260
00:14:00,840 --> 00:14:03,370
I wonder which god will be worshipped inside.

261
00:14:04,400 --> 00:14:05,530
That depends on her.

262
00:14:07,280 --> 00:14:09,210
It depends on the people's choice.

263
00:14:10,640 --> 00:14:12,360
Yunmeng has already bought this place,

264
00:14:12,360 --> 00:14:14,290
and given it to the people for free.

265
00:14:14,560 --> 00:14:16,020
I thought she had no money.

266
00:14:16,440 --> 00:14:17,440
A few days ago,

267
00:14:17,440 --> 00:14:19,880
I failed to figure out my family's situation.

268
00:14:19,880 --> 00:14:21,160
Someone came and told me

269
00:14:21,160 --> 00:14:24,820
that the late emperor once bestowed a copper mine upon our family.

270
00:14:29,000 --> 00:14:31,040
And here I was looking for investors everywhere.

271
00:14:31,040 --> 00:14:34,100
I didn't expect my wealthy backer to be right next to me.

272
00:14:36,600 --> 00:14:37,120
Miss Tu.

273
00:14:37,320 --> 00:14:38,400
You can stay in my humble home

274
00:14:38,400 --> 00:14:39,660
for as long as you want.

275
00:14:40,120 --> 00:14:41,000
If you need anything,

276
00:14:41,000 --> 00:14:42,280
just let me know.

277
00:14:42,800 --> 00:14:43,440
Here you go.

278
00:14:43,440 --> 00:14:44,300
It's all yours.

279
00:14:44,880 --> 00:14:45,680
Young Master.

280
00:14:45,760 --> 00:14:47,640
Then won't I lose sleep every day?

281
00:14:49,240 --> 00:14:51,640
Today's hardship is for tomorrow's glory.

282
00:14:53,480 --> 00:14:54,680
Mr. Liu,

283
00:14:55,200 --> 00:14:57,560
why haven't you visited Baoyue Pavilion for days?

284
00:14:57,560 --> 00:14:59,420
The matter we discussed last time

285
00:14:59,600 --> 00:15:01,000
hasn't been settled yet.

286
00:15:03,560 --> 00:15:05,400
Now that I have a sales channel

287
00:15:05,440 --> 00:15:06,840
and financial support,

288
00:15:07,400 --> 00:15:11,330
becoming the richest man in the Song Dynasty is just around the corner.

289
00:15:14,760 --> 00:15:15,120
Boss,

290
00:15:15,440 --> 00:15:17,170
I'll treat everyone to dinner.

291
00:15:19,600 --> 00:15:20,200
Liu Chuan.

292
00:15:22,840 --> 00:15:24,000
Liu Chuan, why are you hiding?

293
00:15:24,000 --> 00:15:24,880
What are you doing?

294
00:15:24,880 --> 00:15:26,360
What are you doing?

295
00:15:26,360 --> 00:15:27,800
When will you become my personal bodyguard?

296
00:15:27,800 --> 00:15:29,200
Wouldn't that make me your slave?

297
00:15:29,200 --> 00:15:29,640
So what?

298
00:15:29,640 --> 00:15:30,440
Boss, save me!

299
00:15:30,480 --> 00:15:31,080
Liu Chuan.

300
00:15:32,360 --> 00:15:33,600
Save me!

301
00:15:41,640 --> 00:15:42,640
I can save him.

302
00:15:43,480 --> 00:15:45,400
What exactly is that Skull Grass?

303
00:15:47,160 --> 00:15:49,240
I haven't figured it out to this day.

304
00:15:50,280 --> 00:15:52,400
The man who looked for Qu Dayou back then,

305
00:15:52,400 --> 00:15:53,860
do you still remember him?

306
00:15:55,640 --> 00:15:57,080
Strange to say,

307
00:15:57,440 --> 00:15:59,560
I just can't remember his face.

308
00:16:00,280 --> 00:16:01,540
I only remember that he

309
00:16:02,440 --> 00:16:03,840
was luxuriously dressed

310
00:16:04,080 --> 00:16:05,680
with an extraordinary aura.

311
00:16:07,280 --> 00:16:09,540
He truly looked like the God of Medicine.

312
00:16:38,800 --> 00:16:41,600
As expected, he found clues about the Kulou Grass.

313
00:16:41,960 --> 00:16:44,160
Liu Chuan really didn't disappoint me.

314
00:16:44,640 --> 00:16:45,800
In that case,

315
00:16:46,080 --> 00:16:48,400
let's have him do something for us.
